a:2:{s:7:"content";s:417:"<h2>Offering bundle options</h2>
<p>Used books cause financial challenges for publishers...in fact, they are the root cause of the pricing crisis that students and the industry are facing now. “Bundling” books is a win-win: more books at a discount for the students, and new books sold for publishers. In some cases, like this one, two titles are the perfect match to complement one another and sell together.</p>";s:12:"content_meta";N;}